# Operational Scripts & Tools
# 默认忽略 scripts/ 下所有内容，但精确放行内推自动化所需的脚本（用 scripts/* 而非
# scripts/，否则目录被整体忽略时下面的例外规则不会生效）。
scripts/*
!scripts/scrape-byr-enhanced.ts
!scripts/upload-byr-enhanced.ts
!scripts/email-byr-digest.ts
!scripts/scrape-byr-boards.ts
!scripts/upload-byr-board-posts.ts
!scripts/create-byr-board-posts-table.ts
!scripts/sync-referrals.sh
analysis/

